OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry night with clear spells, although
OL,7,Fcloud will tend to thicken overnight,
OL,8,Fespecially in the northwest. A little
OL,9,Fchilly by the end of the night,
OL,10,Fperhaps with isolated fog patches in
OL,11,Fprone spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FDry start with sunny spells,
OL,14,Fbut cloud thickening, with a band of
OL,15,Frain spreading southeast in the
OL,16,Fafternoon. This clearing to colder,
OL,17,Fbreezier and brighter conditions, with
OL,18,Foccasional blustery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
