OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold
OL,6,Fstart Friday, with some frost, then
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. Rain and stronger
OL,8,Fwinds overnight, followed by sunshine
OL,9,Fand blustery showers into Sunday.
OL,10,FFeeling rather cool at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
